Class eRFID_ErrorCodes

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.regula.documentreader.api.enums.eRFID_ErrorCodes

  • public class eRFID_ErrorCodes
extends java.lang.Object
    contains a set of error codes returned by the MCL func-tions or transferred to the user application by the callback-function.
